verses.text:
I will show wonders in the sky above,
and signs on the earth beneath;
blood, and fire, and billows of smoke.

The Lord said to him,
“Arise, and go to the street which is called Straight, and inquire in the house of Judah
for one named Saul, a man of Tarsus. For behold, he is praying,

‘Behold, you scoffers, and wonder, and perish;
for I work a work in your days,
a work which you will in no way believe, if one declares it to you.’”

That the rest of men may seek after the Lord;
all the Gentiles who are called by my name,
says the Lord, who does all these things.
